  "title": "Property Sales Consultant (Basic + Commission) - Property Developer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Generate qualified leads through prospecting, networking, and referrals</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service and guide clients through the property buying and selling process</li>\n  <li>Negotiate and close sales transactions effectively</li>\n  <li>Maintain a strong pipeline of prospective clients and opportunities</li>\n  <li>Stay up-to-date with market trends and property regulations</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the broader sales team to share best practices and support each other's success</li>\n  <li>Ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Relevant qualifications or certifications in real estate (CEA) will be advantageous</li>\n  <li>Proven track record in sales, preferably in the property or real estate industry</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and negotiation skills with the ability to build strong relationships with clients</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, driven, and able to work independently to achieve sales targets</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with the local property market and industry regulations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly click the <strong>APPLY </strong>button below or send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:gs1@talenttradersg.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>salestrader@talenttradersg.com</strong></a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Reg. No.: R24120209 (GAN CHYE SHEN)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
